flowchart TD
    A[Student opens assignment page] --> B[Load assignment types and statuses]
    B --> C[Student selects assignment type]
    C --> D[Student uploads assignment video]
    D --> E[Validate submission]
    E --> F{Valid?}
    F -->|No| G[Show upload or validation error]
    F -->|Yes| H[Create assignment submission]
    H --> I[Set status pending_review]
    I --> J[Trigger assignment review email if enabled]
    J --> K[Show updated assignment status to student]